headline: ICE's Natural Gas and Oil Markets at Record Open Interest
summary: LONDON & AMSTERDAM & NEW YORK, June 30, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data and home of the most liquid energy markets in the world, today announced that its global natural gas and oil markets are at record open interest (OI).
